      "sc:description": "This tool provides an automatic segmentation model for spinal cord lesions in axial T2-weighted MRI scans, designed to improve the accuracy and efficiency of MS research and clinical workflows. The model is available on GitHub and accompanied by documentation and installation instructions.",
